竊佔他人之不動產者，依前\r\n項之規定處斷。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SLDM/111%2c%e5%af%a9%e7%b0%a1%2c643%2c20220927%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SLDM,111,審簡,643,20220927,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"審簡","JNO":"643","JDATE":"20220927","JTITLE":"竊盜"}